  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The majority of kidney stones are treated with shock wave lithotripsy (SWL). We are examining
      if the medication Flomax will result in improved stone passage rates following SWL.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Placebo blinded study examining the effects of Flomax on stone passage rates following SWL.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
